apaxYml.name: @ax/axunit-runner-llvm-win-x64
apaxYml.author: Siemens AG
apaxYml.description: The AxUnit Target. Do not reference this package directly, use @ax/axunit-runner-llvm instead.

build: dotnet publish ../../src/AxUnit.Runner -o bin -r win-x64 -f netcoreapp3.1 -c Release -p:DebugType=None -p:DebugSymbols=false -p:NuGetScannerDownloadSources=false

apaxYml.name: @ax/build-native-winx64
apaxYml.author: Siemens AG
apaxYml.description: tools to compile LLVM to native for winx64

scripts.build:
cp ../../llvm-10.0.0-winx64/bin/clang.exe bin/
cp -r ../../llvm-10.0.0-winx64/lib/clang lib/
cp ../../llvm-10.0.0-winx64/bin/lld-link.exe bin/
cp ../../compile-app/compile-app.js bin/
